channel.title: H. - Aqzi (Plus details)
channel.description:
Hey! First of all I wanna thank each and every one of you for being so supportive to me on this journey I’ve taken. I want to make a few announcements about my music and where you can find it in the future.
As some of you may know, I’ve been deleting old tracks and stuff for the past few months now to try to make more minutes for my Soundcloud page. Unfortunately, I can’t keep doing this, and I can’t afford a pro subscription. So I’ve turned to Spotify. Here you can find my 2nd to latest track [h](https://open.spotify.com/track/6AgjPy7yFplG6APlW7iKvl?si=0u8von__S3yYt9sSLGUEeg), and on July 8th, Quake will drop. I have some tracks in the process of finishing touches at the moment, so expect to hear more from me soon! :]
Thanks, Lex ❤️
